				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">one note about drakes.
<br />

<br />
if you have a large mage force, you can just target a drake, pick a moment and sick all the pets in together at once.  as long as you don't cast directly on the drake others will not add. 
<br />

<br />
HOWEVER- DO NOT USE EPIC PET while doing this technique.  the epic has some kind of ae taunt and other drakes WILL aggro on the epic pet and once it is dead will summon the owner and kill him/her.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
