				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">While I have never had the opportunity to participate in a Pet based raid in PoA.  I do have over a dozen runs to the top under my belt.  Every run so far, we have never done the Undine spirits till last.  Especially when the SotS is up.
<br />

<br />
Just use melee, pets, whatever, and try to keep them positioned so you push the sphinx away from the building.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=126928" target="_blank" class="postlink">Marauder Lojack, Deciever</a>
