				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Yes, you need a raid to get to 7th island.  However, once you establish yourself there, it is fairly simple to leave a necro & cleric camped up there for awhile.  Then you can come back later, or even sell this opportunity to somebody to bring an entire raid directly to 7th island.
<br />

<br />
