<br />

<br />
Shortly after the raid was called, I became Cazic Thule's newest epic mage.  Felt fantastic to finally weild the Orb, especially when I was just 1 item away(Earth Staff) from completing the quest from when I used to play a few years back (recently started playing again with a new mage in July).
<br />

<br />
Also wanted to note the bugged Azarack is still there.  It pathed over the island and our cleric got DT'd.  We petitioned and within 2 mins a GM was there to /kill the Azarack.  Needless to say, we were impressed.  People thought we were on a Legends server. lol
