				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'll have to dig up my screenies and see if I have any of the pics of us clearing 7th isle.
<br />

<br />
It is true,  Epic pet DOES have huge aggro.  We barred our epic mages from using Epic up there because they died every time.  Just below the ramp to the RIGHT ( if you are facing the building ) is where we pulled from.  If you look up you will notice the drakes path.  They make a huge circle around the building.  Simply watch for them to come towards you and they will zig zag back and forth coming down to ground level then turn to there right and move in front of the building.  This is where you DON'T pull...  instead you wait untill they are zig zagging down then send your pet... Everyone sends there pets...  Air pets or MS pets only.  Why?  Because you can not summon any other type of pet in the Plain of Air...   With 6 mages we cleared all the drakes.  Just send pet,  when pet dies,  cast another....  As long as you do not NOOK or get any aggro on drake yourself,  none of the other drakes will bother you.  They will simply fly by like nothing is happening.  I don't know why but when Epic pet was used all the additional drakes would aggro and kill the owner of the epic pet..
<br />

<br />
65 earth pet soloing ?  No you cant...  why?  as stated above you can not cast any pet except MS pets or Air pets.  ( when we did this was before PoP and before anyone could level above level 60.. If something has changed please correct me )
<br />

<br />

<br />
Mukta</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
